    <published>2018-05-06T16:24:17.639Z</published>
    <updated>2018-05-09T16:22:43.589Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>中学阶段数学知识储备。</p><a id="more"></a><h4 id="邻域">1.邻域</h4><h4 id="初等函数">2.初等函数</h4><p>（1） 奇偶性——<span class="math inline">\(y=f(x)(x\in D)\)</span>,D关于原点对称，</p><p><span class="math inline">\(\left\{ \begin{array}{c}f(x)=f(-x)\Rightarrow &amp;\text{f(x)是奇函数}\\ f(x)=-f(-x) \Rightarrow&amp;\text{f(x)是偶函数} \end{array}\right.\)</span></p><p>（2）反函数——<span class="math inline">\(y=f(x)(x\in D)\)</span>,D关于原点对称，则<span class="math inline">\(y=f(x)\Rightarrow x=\phi(y)\)</span>,注意不需要再次替换变量写成<span class="math inline">\(y=f(x)\)</span>的形式。</p><p><strong>eg(0506-1): <span class="math inline">\(y=ln(x+\sqrt[2]{x^2+1})\)</span>,（1）、判断奇偶性（2）、求反函数</strong></p><p>（3）有界性——<span class="math inline">\(y=f(x),(x\in D)\)</span>.若<span class="math inline">\(\exists M&gt;0,\forall x\in D\)</span><code>有</code><span class="math inline">\(|f(x)|\leq M\)</span><code>.则称</code><span class="math inline">\(f(x)\)</span>在D上有界。</p><p><span class="math inline">\(f(x)\geq M_1\)</span>.称<span class="math inline">\(f(x)\)</span>有下界，<span class="math inline">\(f(x)\leq M_2\)</span>,称<span class="math inline">\(f(x)\)</span>有上界</p><p>如：<span class="math inline">\(-2\leq f(x)\leq3 \Rightarrow|f(x)|\leq3\)</span>,即使上下界不一致，也是有界。</p><p>（4）增减性——<span class="math inline">\(y=f(x)(x\in D)\)</span>,若<span class="math inline">\(\forall x_1,x_2 \in D,x_1&lt;x_2\)</span>，有<span class="math inline">\(f(x_1)&lt;f(x_2)\)</span>，称<span class="math inline">\(y=f(x)\)</span>在<span class="math inline">\(x\in D\)</span>上 严格递增。</p><h4 id="几个特殊函数">3.几个特殊函数</h4><p>（1）符号函数。<span class="math inline">\(sgn(x)=\begin{cases} -1,&amp;{x&lt;0}\\0,&amp;{x=0}\\1,&amp;{x&gt;0}\\ \end{cases}\)</span>，如：<span class="math inline">\(|x|=x\cdot sgn(x)\)</span>。</p><p>（2）取整函数。<span class="math inline">\([x]=\begin{cases} k,&amp;{x=k}\\k-1,&amp;{k-1&lt;x&lt;k}\\ \end{cases}\)</span>（<span class="math inline">\(k\in Z\)</span>）</p><p><strong>注：</strong></p><ol type="1"><li><span class="math inline">\([x]\leq x\)</span>;</li><li>​<span class="math inline">\([x+m]=[x]+m\)</span>,(<span class="math inline">\(m\in Z\)</span>);<br></li><li><span class="math inline">\([x+y]\not=[x]+[y]\)</span></li></ol><p>（3）Dirichlet函数。<span class="math inline">\(D(x)= \begin{cases} 1, &amp;\text{$x\in \theta$}\\ 0, &amp;\text{$x\in R \backslash\theta$} \end{cases}\)</span></p>]]></content>
    
